@Soak_This I used this formula to make my recipes! Pick your fav oils and get mixin! So as not to waste I made 8oz batches to start
@Soak_This 8-17% light oils, up to 5% heavy oils/butters, 75-80% h2o, 3-6% emulsifier, up to 3% thickener, about 1% preservative
